task.summary: Default task
Initial Commit

build: Add Entities and Daos
Add Entities and Daos for Term and Course

build: Add Room Database
Add singleton instance of room database.

feat: Add Term Repository
Add TermRepository, created static ExecutorService pool of 4 threads to be used by the application
Implements: TermRepository, Executor Thread Pool

feat: Enhance MainActivity with ViewModel and listeners, refactor DAOs and Entities, update UI themes and layouts
- MainActivity: Added ViewModel for terms, set up button listeners, and added observer for term changes - CourseDao: Simplified updateCourse method to use @Update annotation - Course, Assessment, Term: Refactored fields and methods, added constructors - TermDao: Minor formatting changes - colors.xml: Added new color definitions for Material3 theme - activity_main.xml: Redesigned layout with new buttons - themes.xml: Updated base theme to Material3 and added color attributes - AndroidManifest.xml: Added new activities for TermList, CourseList, and AssessmentList - Removed unused files in .idea/sonarlint directory

feat: Update UI themes, layouts and add RecyclerViews to list activities
This commit includes several changes to the UI of the application. The color scheme in the themes.xml and colors.xml files has been updated to provide a fresh look. The text size in the MainActivity has been increased for better readability.
The layout of the MainActivity, TermListActivity, AssessmentListActivity, and CourseListActivity have been updated to include RecyclerViews for better list management. The FloatingActionButton has been added to the TermListActivity for adding new terms.
The MaterialCardView has been used in the term_list_item.xml for a consistent look and feel. The AndroidManifest.xml has been updated to include the new AddTermActivity and to set parentActivityName for the list activities.
The strings.xml file has been updated to include new string resources required for the updated UI. The misc.xml file has been updated with VisualizationToolProject settings.
Several Java files have been updated to accommodate these changes. The TermAdapter.java and TermViewModel.java have been updated for the RecyclerView in TermListActivity. The Course.java and CourseDao.java have been updated for the RecyclerView in CourseListActivity.
This commit also includes the removal of some files related to the sonarlint issue store.

feat: Enhance UI with color and elevation changes, add button listener in TermListActivity, refactor TermAdapter and Course classes, update AndroidManifest.xml and dbnavigator.xml, remove unused files in .idea/sonarlint directory

- Update Gradle version to 8.2.0, update distributionUrl to use Gradle 8.5, update TermAdapter with new methods and OnItemClickListener, create ItemTouchHelper for swipe to delete functionality in TermListActivity, and update delete method in TermRepository to accept Term object instead of termName. - Refactor TermViewModel and MainActivity, and update close_icon.xml, course_list_item.xml, term_list_item.xml, activity_main.xml, and AndroidManifest.xml.
feat: Add Course and Assessment Repositories, View Models, List Items, Lists, etc.
feat: AddEditCourseActivity layout, Added activities to AndroidManifest, Add Save Menu Items to add/edit layouts,
feat: AddEditCourseActivity everything except saving Courses, Finish CourseListActivity except populating Term Spinner; add Delete Functionality. Finish Layout using MaterialTextInput.
feat: Finish AddEditCourseActivity
feat: Finish AddEditAssessmentActivity
feat: Finish with Courses - Adding, Editing and Deleting.
feat: Finish AssessmentListActivity
feat: Finish AddEditAssessmentActivity and all functionality related to tracking terms, courses and assessments.
feat: Add restriction for a maximum of 5 assessments per course.
feat: Add assessmentStartDate to Assessment and fix throughout app. Finish note_list_item.
feat: Complete SMS and Email Course Notes functionality and add Assessment Start Date back into application. Create CourseNoteViewModel and CourseNoteListActivity.
feat: Add landscape qualifier for CourseNotes page.
feat: Halfway add Alarms and Notifications

feat: Fix Courses and Terms so that RecyclerView Items get restored if they don't get deleted from the database. Add more example Assessments so that they can just add 1 to check functionality for limiting number of Assessments per Course to 5.
feat: Remove Toggle Buttons from AddEditCourseActivity.java, Add buttons to set or cancel Course Start and Course End Alarms.
feat: Go-back point before removing toggle button stuff.

feat: Add date and time pickers for Start and End Course Alarms, Edit Course object to have start and end alarm fields, Save datetime picker info to database and retrieve and put into UI when updating
feat: Add date and time pickers and edit Assessment model for Assessment Start and End Alarms.
